Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.22,0:00:10.96,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}ディートフリート・ブーゲンビリア大佐
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.74,0:00:13.28,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}弟君がお見えになりました
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.43,0:00:16.59,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}よう　ギル
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.21,0:00:21.31,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}元気にしてたか？　相変わらず辛気くさい顔だな
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.99,0:00:23.46,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}父さんそっくりだ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.39,0:00:26.38,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}兄さんこそ相変わらずだ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.53,0:00:28.73,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}その髪　父上が見たら
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.75,0:00:30.63,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}きっと許しはなかった
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.02,0:00:32.79,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}軍刀で切られていただろうに
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.63,0:00:34.50,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}そりゃごめんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.58,0:00:36.40,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}兄さんはいつもそう
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.90,0:00:38.80,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}死んでくれてよかったよ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.01,0:00:45.12,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}悪かった　そんな顔するなよ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.44,0:00:49.89,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}今日はお前の昇格祝いにいいものを持ってきてやったんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.46,0:00:54.41,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}いいか　あくまで武器として使え
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.91,0:00:56.33,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}情けもかけるな
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.27,0:00:59.15,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}開けてみろ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.47,0:01:13.11,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}おい　起きろ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.81,0:01:23.79,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}北東戦域で拾った
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.96,0:01:28.03,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}名前は
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.73,0:01:30.48,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}ヴァイオレット・エヴァーガーデンです
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.81,0:01:34.72,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}今日から自動手記人形の見習いとして働くことになった
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.91,0:01:38.79,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}仕事のこととか　いろいろ教えてやってくれ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.09,0:01:40.07,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}はい
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.01,0:01:45.27,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}表情のないその少女はまるで人形のようだった
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.44,0:01:48.94,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}この職業の名の由来となった
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.68,0:01:52.16,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}機械じかけの人形のように
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.70,0:01:57.40,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}えっと　まずはそうね
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.84,0:02:01.03,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}自動手記人形の仕事についてはどれくらい知ってる
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.56,0:02:05.40,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}依頼者の要望に応じて手紙を代筆する部門だと
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.79,0:02:07.07,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}ホッジンズ中佐…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.47,0:02:09.82,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}いえ　社長に伺いました
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.18,0:02:11.25,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}そのとおり
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.01,0:02:14.08,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}完全に理解したとは言えませんが
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.32,0:02:16.64,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}任務の遂行は可能と思われます
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.71,0:02:21.58,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}そんなに簡単な仕事じゃないわよ　っていうか任務って何
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.83,0:02:24.45,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}アイリス　いいから仕事続けて
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.47,0:02:26.59,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}はい…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.30,0:02:31.98,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}そういえばまだ他のドールを紹介してなかったわね
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.02,0:02:33.97,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}えっとドールっていうのは
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.97,0:02:37.32,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}自動手記人形の略称だと　先日理解しました
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.05,0:02:39.15,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}そのとおり
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.75,0:02:45.00,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}さっきの子　あの子がアイリス　養成講座を終えたばかりの新人ちゃん
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.37,0:02:47.47,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}それから彼女はエリカ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.68,0:02:50.96,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}彼女も私も　ドールは前からやっていたけど
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.24,0:02:56.12,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}うちの会社自体出来てまだ日も浅いから　みんな新入りみたいなものよ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.29,0:02:58.20,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}全然違うと思います
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.42,0:03:03.19,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}ヴァイオレット　あなたタイプライターは使えるんだっけ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.75,0:03:05.55,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}使用したことはありません
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.91,0:03:09.11,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}じゃあまずはタイプの練習から始めましょうか
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.30,0:03:11.04,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}それでドールになるわけ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.27,0:03:13.72,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}アイリス　教則本貸してくれる
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.28,0:03:15.58,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}はい
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.60,0:03:19.83,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}えっと…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.29,0:03:21.39,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}座って
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.75,0:03:22.90,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}了解しました
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.19,0:03:32.01,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}手袋は取ったほうがいいわね
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.30,0:03:33.23,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}はい
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.56,0:03:41.68,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}大丈夫
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.92,0:03:44.24,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}問題ありません
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.67,0:03:48.53,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}そう　じゃあまずはやってみましょうか
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.68,0:03:51.82,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}こうやって紙をセットして
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.06,0:03:54.03,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}ノブを回して巻き込むの
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.32,0:03:58.00,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}FとJにそれぞれ人差し指を置いて打ってみて
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.51,0:03:59.31,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}はい
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.49,0:04:09.18,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}そうそう　その調子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.30,0:04:13.27,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}あとは文字に対応した指の位置を覚えて
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.06,0:04:16.63,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}この教則本どおりに打ってみて
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.67,0:04:46.99,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}ちょっと　ヴァイオレット…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.09,0:04:53.85,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}ヴァイオレット　やめて
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.91,0:05:01.23,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}もう少し
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.29,0:05:04.13,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}静かに　ねッ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.44,0:05:09.87,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}ありがとうございました
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.14,0:05:13.31,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}1.2リブルですので　10コルスでございます
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.35,0:05:17.45,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}ありがとうございました
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.21,0:05:18.55,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}やっとお昼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.57,0:05:19.67,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}ネリネ　リリアン
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.87,0:05:25.39,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}一緒に昼飯食おうぜ　焼きそばお前らの分も買ってあっからよ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.56,0:05:27.58,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}いらない
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.88,0:05:32.61,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}それと　そんな汗臭い格好で窓口に来ないでよね
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.31,0:05:37.33,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}いやもう何だあれ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.61,0:05:40.14,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}真面目に汗水垂らして働く男に
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.39,0:05:42.31,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}お疲れ様のひと言もない
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.47,0:05:45.33,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}つか来るなって何だよ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.59,0:05:49.33,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}最近の女の計算高さったら何　香水臭えし
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.65,0:05:53.53,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}あいつらぜってえ窓口に来る金持ち引っかけるつもりなんだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.93,0:05:55.71,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}まあいいじゃないか
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.93,0:05:59.07,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}もういい　もう働く女はいいわ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.37,0:06:00.61,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}お前ら焼きそば
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.62,0:06:01.52,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}いりません
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.80,0:06:03.99,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}それとお前って言うのやめてください
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.03,0:06:10.84,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}焼きそば　わし食うよ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.87,0:06:16.14,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}今日も一日中宛名書きか
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.73,0:06:21.17,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}午後に予約が入ってる２件とも　カトレアさんをご指名ですって
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.46,0:06:23.64,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}大丈夫
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.93,0:06:26.08,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}大丈夫です
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.70,0:06:29.39,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}せっかくライデンに出てきて　ドールになったのに
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.68,0:06:32.35,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}毎日毎日　宛名書きだの
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.53,0:06:36.24,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}戦争で行方不明になった人の安否問い合わせの手紙だの
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.51,0:06:37.87,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}そんなのばっかり
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.51,0:06:39.11,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}そうね
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.38,0:06:43.49,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}そういえば　あの新入りも軍にいたそうですよ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.48,0:06:46.03,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}まだ子供なのに
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.37,0:06:48.40,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}それて…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.15,0:06:51.12,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}何もドールにすることないのに
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.58,0:06:54.35,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}愛想もないし　気も利きそうにないし
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.56,0:06:56.81,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}絶対向いてないですよね
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.86,0:07:00.41,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}もっとワクワクするような手紙が書きたいな
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.70,0:07:04.39,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}有名人の代筆とか　舞台女優の秘密の恋文とか
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.85,0:07:08.23,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}でもそういうのはカトレアさんのとこいっちゃいますもんね
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.18,0:07:12.58,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}ヴァイオレットちゃん　どう
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.15,0:07:15.40,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}お昼に誘ったんだけど
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.54,0:07:19.13,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}補給は不要だっで　ひたすらタイプ練習してる
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.69,0:07:23.83,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}そうだ　面倒かけるね
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.36,0:07:31.28,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}ねえ　じゃあ今度夕食ごちそうしてよ　クラウディア
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.29,0:07:32.70,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}名前で呼ぶな
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.16,0:07:35.97,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}女の子が欲しかったからってあんまりよね
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.11,0:07:39.36,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}ベッドの中で女の名前呼ぶなんて　最悪だったわ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.09,0:07:42.45,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}やめて　お願い　ごめんなさい
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.46,0:07:46.28,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}すぐには無理だな
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.62,0:07:49.07,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}今月の俺の給料なしだから
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.11,0:08:07.09,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}宛名書き　終わりました
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.39,0:08:08.63,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}お疲れさま
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.80,0:08:10.60,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}配達のほうに回しておきます
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.70,0:08:12.02,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}うん　お願い
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.75,0:08:15.79,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}ヴァイオレットもお疲れさま　今日はもう終わりにして
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.69,0:08:17.66,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}どれどれ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.53,0:08:21.46,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}ずいぶん上達したじゃない　すごいわ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.97,0:08:23.83,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}すごいのはこの武器です
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.19,0:08:25.16,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}武器…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.52,0:08:30.68,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}そうよね　私たち働く女性が社会に出て戦うためのね
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.22,0:08:32.82,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}明日は誰かの横で
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.90,0:08:35.03,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}実際のドールの仕事を見ていこっか
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.71,0:08:38.36,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}私はこれから出張サービスにいってくるの
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.72,0:08:42.93,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}要望があれば　自宅や仕事先にも出向いて代筆するのよ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.20,0:08:47.99,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}私も携帯してよろしいでしょうか
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.19,0:08:50.13,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}タイプを　どこへ？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.65,0:08:53.41,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}自室です　訓練のためと
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.89,0:08:55.08,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}それから…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.91,0:09:11.28,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}住所？　ギルベルトの？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.54,0:09:15.71,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}はい　代筆業務に着任し　訓練を開始したと
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.84,0:09:17.79,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}現状報告をしたいのです
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.20,0:09:24.35,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}少佐はまだお忙しく　お目にかかれる状況ではないのですよね
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.26,0:09:26.56,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}ああ…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.23,0:09:32.04,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}分かった　これは俺が出しておくよ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.04,0:09:35.64,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}それで　訓練は順調なの
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.79,0:09:38.61,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}順調です　問題ありません
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.25,0:09:44.16,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}知ってのとおり　毎日生活するのもやっとで
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.69,0:09:47.03,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}ご存じのとおり　生活資金にも窮する状況
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.07,0:09:48.90,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}つづりが間違っています
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.11,0:09:54.43,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}それから　毎月2クロルずつ返すって書いてくれ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.39,0:09:56.15,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}毎月…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.35,0:10:00.49,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}2クロルずつですと　完済するまでに120年ほどかかります
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.91,0:10:04.06,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}旦那様はそれまで生存可能なのでしょうか
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.36,0:10:07.34,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}ふだんはすごくいい子なの
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.73,0:10:10.58,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}でも時々カッとなることがあって
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.88,0:10:14.29,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}大切なお子様にケガをさせてしまいましたことを…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.68,0:10:16.95,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}私のしつけが悪かったのかしら…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.10,0:10:19.09,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}私どもの日頃の指導が…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.12,0:10:19.83,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}何が…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.57,0:10:23.03,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}何がいけなかったの
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.18,0:10:24.14,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}あの…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.34,0:10:28.17,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}業務が滞りますので　即座に泣くのを中断してください
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.32,0:10:28.83,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}ちょ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.56,0:10:32.43,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}何だよこの文章は
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.82,0:10:35.28,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}勝手なお願いではございますが
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.52,0:10:36.96,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}勝手なって何だよ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.43,0:10:38.83,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}すみません
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.07,0:10:42.01,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}遅れにつきましては　弁解の余地もなく
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.20,0:10:44.77,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}これじゃ俺がまるっきり悪いみてえじゃねえか
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.08,0:10:46.58,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}お前何様だ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.88,0:10:48.19,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}エリカ様です
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.78,0:10:50.45,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}名前なんて聞いてねえ！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.68,0:10:53.15,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}とにかく　この手紙は気に入らねえ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.41,0:10:54.84,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}金は払わねえからな
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.45,0:10:58.81,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}気に入らないから代金を支払わないは違法行為です
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.09,0:11:01.92,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}どこがどのように気に入らないのか
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.02,0:11:03.12,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}どけよ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.51,0:11:05.87,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}具体的かつ　適切な指示を
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.83,0:11:08.34,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}速やかにしてください
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.55,0:11:15.23,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}お客様から何件か苦情が来てるんだけど
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.92,0:11:17.24,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}問題がありましたか
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.54,0:11:19.13,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}いや　まあ…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.65,0:11:20.95,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}君は大丈夫
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.87,0:11:23.60,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}健康には異常ありません
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.83,0:11:26.96,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}いや　そのドールの仕事のほうは…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.43,0:11:28.91,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}鋭意訓練中です
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.75,0:11:30.67,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}そっか
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.23,0:11:31.83,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}あの…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.62,0:11:35.23,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}このあと予約のお客様はいらっしゃいません
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.61,0:11:40.12,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}商工会議所の名簿の作成を彼女と鋭意行いますので
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.14,0:11:46.81,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}会社と住所　それから業種をタイプして
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.87,0:11:48.02,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}了解しました
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.28,0:11:57.71,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}ねえ　あなたどうしてこの仕事をしたいの
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.29,0:12:00.30,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}私は…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.63,0:12:01.40,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}あら
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.13,0:12:03.40,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}誰もいないの
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.53,0:12:05.55,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}いらっしゃいませ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.84,0:12:07.51,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}代筆をご希望でございますか
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.25,0:12:11.84,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}他に何の用が
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.22,0:12:13.41,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}失礼いたしました
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.89,0:12:18.48,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}お客様がお望みなら　どのような文章も代筆させていただきます
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.98,0:12:21.04,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}自動手記人形サービス　エ…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.04,0:12:22.75,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}カトレア・ボードレルってドールは
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.46,0:12:25.17,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}ただいま出張しております
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.64,0:12:28.88,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}あら　彼女なら間違いないって聞いて来たのに
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.40,0:12:30.55,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}まあいいわ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.20,0:12:33.94,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}私ね交際を申し込まれたの
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.25,0:12:36.73,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}自動車の会社を立ち上げた男性でね
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.01,0:12:39.37,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}これから自家用車の時代だからって
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.86,0:12:40.92,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}はあ…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.15,0:12:44.85,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}でもね　私そんな簡単な女じゃないし
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.28,0:12:47.40,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}尻の軽い女に見られたくないわけ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.49,0:12:50.43,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}あの　つまり…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.71,0:12:52.94,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}まあ　大した男じゃないし
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.43,0:12:55.38,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}私には好意なんてないけど
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.99,0:12:58.12,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}彼がもっと誠意を見せてくれて
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.26,0:13:00.79,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}本当に私を愛してるなら
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.23,0:13:05.59,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}気品のあるロマンチックな手紙をお願い
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.18,0:13:07.14,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}書いといて
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.76,0:13:09.67,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}その…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.97,0:13:19.04,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}あら　あなたが書いてくれるの
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.09,0:13:21.18,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}了解しました
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.46,0:13:37.07,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}何なの　あの手紙
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.39,0:13:40.14,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}お客様　どうぞ落ち着いてください
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.58,0:13:42.27,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}アイリス　お茶をお出しして
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.43,0:13:43.29,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}はい
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.42,0:13:46.28,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}ご要望どおりに代筆しました
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.67,0:13:48.08,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}あれのどこが
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.19,0:13:50.90,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}彼怒って手紙を送り返してきたのよ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.91,0:13:53.14,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}読んでみなさいよ　自分が書いたやつ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.17,0:13:57.03,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}手紙を拝読しましたが
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.24,0:13:59.63,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}私には現在好意はありません
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.16,0:14:03.95,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}なおかつ　貴殿の誠意も愛情も不足しています
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.37,0:14:08.23,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}私は複雑かつ重々しい女でありますので
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.51,0:14:15.93,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}その点を考慮し　贈答品および資金を調達したうえ再度の挑戦を要望します
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.91,0:14:19.77,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}どこが間違っていたのでしょうか
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.57,0:14:22.10,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}申し訳ありません
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.37,0:14:25.03,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}ちょっと表現が素直すぎたというか…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.85,0:14:29.70,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}わたし彼とお付き合いしたかったの
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.31,0:14:32.73,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}でも彼の思いをすぐに受け入れたら
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.88,0:14:35.17,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}簡単に手にいる女だって思われるじゃない
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.96,0:14:39.50,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}もっと追いかけてほしいのが女ってもんでしょ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.70,0:14:42.31,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}私だって愛してたのよ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.09,0:14:52.01,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}何にする
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.21,0:14:56.49,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}水分の補給には　水か白湯で十分です
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.41,0:14:59.90,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}花茶を2つ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.19,0:15:01.21,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}かしこまりました
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.92,0:15:08.09,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}あなたにいきなり任せる仕事じゃなかったわね
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.84,0:15:10.07,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}理解不能です
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.20,0:15:15.17,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}依頼者の意図を最大限反映して文章を記しました
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.58,0:15:21.13,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}言葉には裏と表があるの
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.03,0:15:24.35,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}口に出したことがすべてじゃないのよ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.63,0:15:27.65,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}人の弱いところね
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.75,0:15:31.80,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}相手を試すことで　自分の存在を確認するの
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.35,0:15:36.72,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}裏腹よね
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.57,0:15:46.51,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}やっぱり私だけで送り先の彼の所へ行って謝ってくるわ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.15,0:16:00.07,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}少佐…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.37,0:16:05.40,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}少佐
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.34,0:16:09.83,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}ギルベルト少佐
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.46,0:16:24.17,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}おい
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.88,0:16:27.98,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}どうした　1人か？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.47,0:16:32.24,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}元気ねえな　飯ちゃんと食ってるか
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.87,0:16:34.53,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}栄養の補給はしています
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.51,0:16:39.19,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}じゃあ　仕事の失敗でもしたか
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.91,0:16:45.61,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}お前配達に戻ってこいよ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.49,0:16:49.34,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}配達業務ではダメなのです
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.42,0:16:56.67,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}ドールの仕事にこだわんないで　ほかの仕事探したほうがいいんじゃねえの
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.24,0:17:00.39,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}俺も考えよう
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.89,0:17:04.24,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}ホッジンズのヤツ今月給料ねえっつってたし
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.53,0:17:06.31,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}うちの会社ヤバいかもな
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.89,0:17:33.75,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}質問よろしいでしょうか
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.38,0:17:39.79,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}私は自動手記人形に不適格でしょうか
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.92,0:17:44.20,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}それは私も…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.21,0:17:45.95,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}あなたのことは聞いていません
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.61,0:17:54.27,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}向いてないわ　第一あなたどうしてこの仕事がいいのよ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.04,0:18:01.13,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}愛してるを知りたいのです
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.47,0:18:04.41,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}それだけ？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.55,0:18:05.57,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}それだけです
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.99,0:18:11.20,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}特定の感情を表す言葉だと理解はしているのですが
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.00,0:18:16.96,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}少佐がなぜ私に向けて　突然その言葉を口にしたのか
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.99,0:18:20.27,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}知りたいのです
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.47,0:18:23.20,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}たとえ向いていなくても
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.13,0:18:27.59,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}私はこの仕事を続けたいのです
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.02,0:18:40.83,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}更衣室にタオルがあるから
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.97,0:18:43.68,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}どちらにせよ　彼女…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.02,0:18:46.19,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}ヴァイオレットにドールは無理だと思います
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.04,0:18:49.02,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}うちはまだ出来たばかりの会社ですが
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.26,0:18:51.09,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}カトレアさんへの依頼は絶えません
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.71,0:18:54.45,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}でも　ここで評判が落ちたりしたら
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.66,0:18:56.65,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}せっかく軌道に乗ってきてるのに…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.27,0:18:58.88,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}ヴァイオレットには辞めてもらったほうが
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.32,0:19:00.90,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}いや　もう少し…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.39,0:19:02.25,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}あの
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.23,0:19:06.29,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}エリカ　てかヴァイオレットちゃんも
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.75,0:19:08.21,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}どうしたの　2人とも
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.01,0:19:10.81,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}何も…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.41,0:19:13.97,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}何も辞めさせることはないと思います
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.07,0:19:19.25,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}彼女　ヴァイオレットは　タイプは正確で速いですし
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.65,0:19:22.88,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}宛名書きや名簿の作成といった業務はこなせます
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.63,0:19:27.07,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}そのうち　もっといろんなことを知って
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.03,0:19:31.09,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}手紙も少しずつ書けるようになると思います
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.39,0:19:36.91,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}お願いします　辞めさせないでください
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.43,0:19:39.35,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}裏腹です
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.71,0:19:43.27,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}私はこの任務に向いていないと言ったのに
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.57,0:19:45.55,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}裏腹です
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.49,0:19:59.31,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}自動手記人形に向いていないのは私のほうだ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.59,0:20:04.79,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}だから彼女をあんなにムキになってかばってしまったんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.28,0:20:12.26,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}後のタイプライターとなったその機械は
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.92,0:20:17.23,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}活版印刷の権威である　オーランド博士が発明したものだった
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.60,0:20:23.94,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}小説家でありながら盲目となり執筆できなくなった妻
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.20,0:20:26.45,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}モリーのために制作したものだが
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.30,0:20:30.81,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}博士はそのを自動手記人形と呼んだ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.78,0:20:35.82,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}それが今では代筆業のことを指す呼び名となっている
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.71,0:20:38.87,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}あの子と出会って実感した
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.39,0:20:42.01,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}忘れそうになってた自分の夢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.77,0:20:46.06,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}埋もれてしまってた自分の気持ち
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.59,0:20:51.39,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}オーランド夫人が書いた小説が私の心を震わせたように
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.72,0:20:55.80,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}閉めるけど　いいかい
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.10,0:20:56.67,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}はい
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.65,0:21:03.20,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}私もいつか
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.25,0:21:11.04,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}人の心を動かすようなステキな手紙を書きたい
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.36,0:21:18.57,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}できた
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.81,0:21:20.51,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}どう
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.40,0:21:24.20,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}うん
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.41,0:21:26.31,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}ヴァイオレットちゃん　立ってごらん
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.77,0:21:27.39,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}はい
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.55,0:21:36.81,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}うん　よく似合ってるよ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.21,0:21:39.78,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}やっぱり俺の見立てに間違いはなかった
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.04,0:21:43.70,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}それから　最後にこれ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.51,0:21:45.65,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}遅くなってごめんね
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.18,0:21:49.05,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}開けてごらん
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.45,0:21:52.09,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}開けます
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.31,0:21:57.09,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}これです
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.90,0:21:59.90,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}少佐がくださったブローチです
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.42,0:22:02.35,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}闇市に流れていたんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.64,0:22:05.42,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}誰かが君の荷物から盗んだんだろうな
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.83,0:22:15.07,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}そうだわ　ヴァイオレット
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.29,0:22:17.87,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}あなたドールの育成講座に通ってみない
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.01,0:22:21.99,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}短期の講座もあるし　アイリスも通ってたのよ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.29,0:22:24.95,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}先生すっごく厳しいけどね
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.17,0:22:26.65,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}ためになると思うの
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.77,0:22:33.79,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}あれを買い戻したから今月のお給料なくなったのね
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.41,0:22:36.03,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}いただきます
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.71,0:22:42.49,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}ねえ　あの子の言う少佐って誰のこと
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.83,0:22:49.14,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}ギルベルト
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.18,0:22:54.47,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}士官学校時代からの友人だ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.35,0:22:57.14,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}ブーゲンビリア家の一族で
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.32,0:22:59.63,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}ああ　あの辺境伯の…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.39,0:23:09.42,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}いいとこの坊ちゃんのわりには
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.68,0:23:11.23,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}骨のあるヤツだったよ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.87,0:23:12.92,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}だった？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.40,0:23:36.33,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}あいつはもう
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,ch
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.22,0:00:10.96,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}迪特福利特·布干維爾大佐
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.74,0:00:13.28,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}您弟弟前來拜訪
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.43,0:00:16.59,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}你好啊 基爾
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.21,0:00:21.31,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}最近可好？ 還是一如既往的一臉煩悶啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.99,0:00:23.46,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}和爸爸一模一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.39,0:00:26.38,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}大哥才是一點沒變啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.53,0:00:28.73,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}你的頭髮要是被父親看到了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.75,0:00:30.63,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}一定不會原諒你的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.02,0:00:32.79,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}明明用軍刀割斷過一次了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.63,0:00:34.50,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}那還真是不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.58,0:00:36.40,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}大哥你總是這個樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.90,0:00:38.80,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}還好他死了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.01,0:00:45.12,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}抱歉 別這副表情
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.44,0:00:49.89,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}今天為了慶祝你晉升 給你帶了好禮物
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.46,0:00:54.41,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}聽好了 最多作為武器使用
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.91,0:00:56.33,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}不要心生憐憫
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.27,0:00:59.15,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}打開看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.47,0:01:13.11,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}喂 醒醒
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.81,0:01:23.79,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}在東北戰區撿到的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.96,0:01:28.03,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}名字叫
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.73,0:01:30.48,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}我是薇爾莉特·伊芙加登
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.81,0:01:34.72,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}今天開始作為見習自動手記人偶在這裡工作
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.91,0:01:38.79,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}工作方面多帶帶她
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.09,0:01:40.07,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}好的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.01,0:01:45.27,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}那位少女面無表情 彷彿人偶一般
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.44,0:01:48.94,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}就像這個職業名稱的由來
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.68,0:01:52.16,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}機械裝置的人偶一般
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.70,0:01:57.40,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}嗯 那麼首先
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.84,0:02:01.03,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}自動手記人偶的工作 你了解多少呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.56,0:02:05.40,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}是根據委託人的請求 代筆寫信的部門
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.79,0:02:07.07,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}霍金斯中佐…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.47,0:02:09.82,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}不 社長是這麼說的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.18,0:02:11.25,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}就是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.01,0:02:14.08,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}雖然說不上完全理解
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.32,0:02:16.64,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}但還是可以執行任務的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.71,0:02:21.58,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}這工作哪有這麼簡單 再說什麼叫「任務」
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.83,0:02:24.45,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}愛麗絲 行了 繼續工作
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.47,0:02:26.59,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}是…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.30,0:02:31.98,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}說起來還沒介紹其他的人偶吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.02,0:02:33.97,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}所謂人偶就是說…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.97,0:02:37.32,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}自動手記人偶的簡稱 之前理解了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.05,0:02:39.15,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.75,0:02:45.00,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}剛才那位就是愛麗絲 剛上完培訓講座的新人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.37,0:02:47.47,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}然後這位是埃麗卡
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.68,0:02:50.96,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}她和我一樣 雖然之前都做過人偶的工作
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.24,0:02:56.12,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}不過我們公司才成立不久 大家都像新人一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.29,0:02:58.20,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}我倒覺得完全不一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.42,0:03:03.19,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}薇爾莉特 你會用打字機嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.75,0:03:05.55,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}沒有使用經驗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.91,0:03:09.11,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}那先從練習打字開始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.30,0:03:11.04,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}就這樣還當人偶？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.27,0:03:13.72,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}愛麗絲 借下教材可以嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.28,0:03:15.58,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.60,0:03:19.83,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.29,0:03:21.39,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}坐吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.75,0:03:22.90,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}明白
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.19,0:03:32.01,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}把手套摘了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.30,0:03:33.23,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.56,0:03:41.68,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}沒關係嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.92,0:03:44.24,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}沒問題
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.67,0:03:48.53,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}是嗎 那先試試看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.68,0:03:51.82,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}像這樣把紙固定好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.06,0:03:54.03,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}轉動旋鈕把紙捲進去
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.32,0:03:58.00,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}把食指放在「Ｆ」和「J」上 打打看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.51,0:03:59.31,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.49,0:04:09.18,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}沒錯 就是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.30,0:04:13.27,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}接下來記住字母對應的手指的位置吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.06,0:04:16.63,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}照著這本教材打打看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.67,0:04:46.99,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}等一下 薇爾莉特…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.09,0:04:53.85,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}薇爾莉特 停下
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.91,0:05:01.23,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}稍微再
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.29,0:05:04.13,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}輕一點 好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.44,0:05:09.87,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}多謝惠顧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.14,0:05:13.31,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}總計1.2里布爾 一共10考斯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.35,0:05:17.45,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5\an8}多謝惠顧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.21,0:05:18.55,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}總算午休了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.57,0:05:19.67,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}娜麗 莉蓮
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.87,0:05:25.39,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}一起吃午飯吧 炒麵也買了你們倆的份
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.56,0:05:27.58,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}不需要
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.88,0:05:32.61,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}還有 別滿頭大汗地來我們接待窗口啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.31,0:05:37.33,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}我就搞不懂了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.61,0:05:40.14,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}面對認真工作滿頭大汗的男人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.39,0:05:42.31,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}一句「辛苦你了」也不說
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.47,0:05:45.33,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}再說「別來」是什麼鬼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.59,0:05:49.33,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}最近的女生也太心機了 一股香水味
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.65,0:05:53.53,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}那些傢伙絕對是想釣來窗口辦事的有錢人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.93,0:05:55.71,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}這不也挺好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.93,0:05:59.07,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}受夠了 職場女性就算了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.37,0:06:00.61,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}你倆吃炒麵嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.62,0:06:01.52,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}不要
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.80,0:06:03.99,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}還有別那樣叫我們
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.03,0:06:10.84,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}炒麵 我吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.87,0:06:16.14,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}今天也要填一整天的收件人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.73,0:06:21.17,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}下午的兩件預約 也都點名讓嘉德麗雅去辦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.46,0:06:23.64,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.93,0:06:26.08,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.70,0:06:29.39,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}好不容易來了萊頓 當上了人偶
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.68,0:06:32.35,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}每天不是填收件人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.53,0:06:36.24,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}就是寫信打聽戰爭中失蹤的人是否安好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.51,0:06:37.87,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}淨是這種事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.51,0:06:39.11,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.38,0:06:43.49,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}說起來 那個新人好像也是從軍隊裡來的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.48,0:06:46.03,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}明明還是個孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.37,0:06:48.40,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}難怪才會…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.15,0:06:51.12,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}那也用不著當人偶吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.58,0:06:54.35,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}待人又不親切 為人也不機靈
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.56,0:06:56.81,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}肯定不適合幹這個的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.86,0:07:00.41,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}真想多寫點讓人心跳的信件啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.70,0:07:04.39,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}給名人代筆 或者舞台劇女演員的秘密情書
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.85,0:07:08.23,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}可是這種事情都交給嘉德麗雅了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.18,0:07:12.58,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}薇爾莉特 怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.15,0:07:15.40,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}我邀請她一起吃午飯了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.54,0:07:19.13,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}可她說不需要補給 埋頭練習打字
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.69,0:07:23.83,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}這樣啊 給你們添麻煩了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.36,0:07:31.28,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}話說 下次就請我吃晚飯吧 克勞迪亞
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.29,0:07:32.70,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}別叫我名字
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.16,0:07:35.97,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}就算你父母再想要女兒 給你起這樣的名字也過分了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.11,0:07:39.36,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}居然要在床上叫女性的名字 真糟糕
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.09,0:07:42.45,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}別這樣 求你了 我錯了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.46,0:07:46.28,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}最近是不行了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.62,0:07:49.07,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}我這個月的工資都沒了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.11,0:08:07.09,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}收件人填完了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.39,0:08:08.63,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}辛苦你了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.80,0:08:10.60,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}我拿去給送信處
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.70,0:08:12.02,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}麻煩啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.75,0:08:15.79,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}薇爾莉特也辛苦了 今天就到這裡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.69,0:08:17.66,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}我看看
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.53,0:08:21.46,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}進步了不少啊 真厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.97,0:08:23.83,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}厲害的是這個武器
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.19,0:08:25.16,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}武器…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.52,0:08:30.68,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}是啊 是我們職場女性在社會中戰鬥的武器啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.22,0:08:32.82,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}明天到別人邊上
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.90,0:08:35.03,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}看看人偶的工作是如何實際操作的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.71,0:08:38.36,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}我接下來要去外出服務
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.72,0:08:42.93,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}只要客戶需要 可以前往客戶家中和單位代筆
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.20,0:08:47.99,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}我也能帶走嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.19,0:08:50.13,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}打字機嗎 帶去哪裡？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.65,0:08:53.41,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}自己房間 為了訓練
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.89,0:08:55.08,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}還有…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.91,0:09:11.28,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}地址？基爾伯特的？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.54,0:09:15.71,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}是的 現已就職代筆工作 開始訓練
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.84,0:09:17.79,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}我想向他匯報現狀
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.20,0:09:24.35,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}少佐現在還忙 還沒辦法拜訪他吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.26,0:09:26.56,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.23,0:09:32.04,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}知道了 那我幫你發出去
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.04,0:09:35.64,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}那麼 「訓練」還順利嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.79,0:09:38.61,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}很順利 沒問題
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.25,0:09:44.16,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}你也知道 每天生活都緊巴巴的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.69,0:09:47.03,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}如您所知 生活資金方面很緊張
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.07,0:09:48.90,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}拼錯詞了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.11,0:09:54.43,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}然後 就寫每個月還2克羅爾
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.39,0:09:56.15,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}每個月…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.35,0:10:00.49,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}2克羅爾的話 要花120年才能還清
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.91,0:10:04.06,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}老爺您能活到那個時候嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.36,0:10:07.34,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}平時是非常聽話的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.73,0:10:10.58,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}可有的時候會突然發火
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.88,0:10:14.29,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}對於讓您心愛的孩子受傷一事…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.68,0:10:16.95,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}是我沒教好嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.10,0:10:19.09,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}是我們平時教育不到位所致…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.12,0:10:19.83,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}到底…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.57,0:10:23.03,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}到底哪裡做錯了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.18,0:10:24.14,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.34,0:10:28.17,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}您中斷了業務 請立刻停止哭泣
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.32,0:10:28.83,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}喂
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.56,0:10:32.43,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}這寫的什麼鬼玩意兒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.82,0:10:35.28,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}「我有個不情之請」
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.52,0:10:36.96,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}「不請」是什麼鬼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.43,0:10:38.83,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}對不起…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.07,0:10:42.01,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}「延期一事 實在無言辯駁」？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.20,0:10:44.77,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}這樣不就說得像都是我的錯了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.08,0:10:46.58,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}你當你是誰啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.88,0:10:48.19,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}她是埃麗卡
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.78,0:10:50.45,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}我沒問她名字！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.68,0:10:53.15,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}總之 這封信我不滿意
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.41,0:10:54.84,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}我不會付錢的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.45,0:10:58.81,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}不滿意就不付錢是違法行為
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.09,0:11:01.92,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}到底哪裡讓您不滿意了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.02,0:11:03.12,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}你閃開
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.51,0:11:05.87,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}具體的 且明確的指示
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.83,0:11:08.34,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}請您立刻提出來
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.55,0:11:15.23,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}客人發來了幾份投訴
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.92,0:11:17.24,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}有什麼問題嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.54,0:11:19.13,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}怎麼說呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.65,0:11:20.95,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}你沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.87,0:11:23.60,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}身體方面沒有異常
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.83,0:11:26.96,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}不 我是指人偶的工作方面…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.43,0:11:28.91,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}正在積極訓練
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.75,0:11:30.67,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.23,0:11:31.83,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.62,0:11:35.23,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}接下來沒有其他客人預約了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.61,0:11:40.12,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}我要和她專心製作工商聯合會的名簿
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.14,0:11:46.81,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}公司和地址 還有行業種類打出來
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.87,0:11:48.02,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}明白
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.28,0:11:57.71,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}我說 你為什麼想做這份工作
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.29,0:12:00.30,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}我…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.63,0:12:01.40,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}哎呀
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.13,0:12:03.40,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}沒有人在嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.53,0:12:05.55,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}歡迎光臨
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.84,0:12:07.51,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}請問是來委託代筆的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.25,0:12:11.84,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}還能有其他事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.22,0:12:13.41,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}失禮了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.89,0:12:18.48,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}只要客人需要 任何文章都能代筆
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.98,0:12:21.04,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}自動手記人偶服務 埃…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.04,0:12:22.75,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}那位嘉德麗雅·波德萊爾人偶呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.46,0:12:25.17,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}她正在出差
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.64,0:12:28.88,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}哎呀 我是聽說找她準沒錯才來的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.40,0:12:30.55,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}不過算了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.20,0:12:33.94,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}有人向我告白了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.25,0:12:36.73,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}他是一家汽車公司的創始人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.01,0:12:39.37,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}還說以後將是私家車的時代
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.86,0:12:40.92,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}是…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.15,0:12:44.85,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}可是呢 我也不是那麼單純的女人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.28,0:12:47.40,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}不想讓他覺得我很輕浮
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.49,0:12:50.43,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}那麼 您的意思是…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.71,0:12:52.94,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}反正也不是很優秀的男人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.43,0:12:55.38,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}雖然我對他沒什麼好感
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.99,0:12:58.12,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}但如果他能再展現些誠意來
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.26,0:13:00.79,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}表示真心愛著我的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.23,0:13:05.59,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}請寫出一封高雅又浪漫的信
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.18,0:13:07.14,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}寫吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.76,0:13:09.67,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.97,0:13:19.04,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}哎呀 你來給我寫嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.09,0:13:21.18,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.46,0:13:37.07,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}那封信寫的什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.39,0:13:40.14,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}這位客人 請先冷靜一下
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.58,0:13:42.27,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}愛麗絲 快去倒杯茶來
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.43,0:13:43.29,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}啊 是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.42,0:13:46.28,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}我已經按照您的要求完成代寫
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.67,0:13:48.08,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}這哪照我要求寫了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.19,0:13:50.90,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}他生氣到把信退回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.91,0:13:53.14,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}你念念看自己都寫了些什麼東西
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.17,0:13:57.03,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}我已拜讀您的來信
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.24,0:13:59.63,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}但我目前對您並沒有好感
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.16,0:14:03.95,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}而且 閣下的誠意及愛意均不足
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.37,0:14:08.23,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}我是心思複雜且穩重的女性
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.51,0:14:15.93,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}請考慮到這點 準備好禮品和禮金後再來挑戰
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.91,0:14:19.77,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}請問哪裡弄錯了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.57,0:14:22.10,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}非常抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.37,0:14:25.03,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}是寫得過於直白了…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.85,0:14:29.70,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}我是想和他交往的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.31,0:14:32.73,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}但我如果立刻接受他的心意
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.88,0:14:35.17,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}不就會讓他覺得我很好搞定嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.96,0:14:39.50,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}女人不就希望多被追求一下嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.70,0:14:42.31,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}我其實也愛著他啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.09,0:14:52.01,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}想喝什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.21,0:14:56.49,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}要補充水分 涼水或者開水就夠了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.41,0:14:59.90,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}兩杯花茶
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.19,0:15:01.21,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}好的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.92,0:15:08.09,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}不該讓你一上來就做那種工作的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.84,0:15:10.07,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}我無法理解
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.20,0:15:15.17,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}我已經寫出最大程度反映委託人意圖的信了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.58,0:15:21.13,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}人的話語有表裡兩層
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.03,0:15:24.35,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}說出口的並不代表全部
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.63,0:15:27.65,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}這就是人類的弱點
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.75,0:15:31.80,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}通過試探他人 來確認自己在對方心中的地位
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.35,0:15:36.72,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}很矛盾吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.57,0:15:46.51,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}我還是單獨去那位先生那裡道歉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.15,0:16:00.07,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}少佐…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.37,0:16:05.40,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}少佐
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.34,0:16:09.83,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}基爾伯特少佐
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.46,0:16:24.17,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}喂
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.88,0:16:27.98,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}怎麼了 就你一個人嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.47,0:16:32.24,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}沒精神呢 有好好吃飯嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.87,0:16:34.53,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}有補充營養
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.51,0:16:39.19,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}那麼 是工作不順利嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.91,0:16:45.61,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}你還是回來送件吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.49,0:16:49.34,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}送件業務不行
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.42,0:16:56.67,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}別執著於人偶的工作 去找其他工作不好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.24,0:17:00.39,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}我也要考慮下了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.89,0:17:04.24,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}霍金斯那傢伙還說他這個月沒工資了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.53,0:17:06.31,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}我們公司情況可能不妙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.89,0:17:33.75,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}我可以問你個問題嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.38,0:17:39.79,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}我是不是不適合當自動手記人偶
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.92,0:17:44.20,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}我也是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.21,0:17:45.95,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}沒有問你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.61,0:17:54.27,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}不適合 況且你為什麼想做這份工作
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.04,0:18:01.13,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}我想知道 「愛著你」的意義
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.47,0:18:04.41,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}就為了這個？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.55,0:18:05.57,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}就因為這個
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.99,0:18:11.20,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}雖然我明白它表達了一種特定的感情
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.00,0:18:16.96,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}但是少佐為什麼突然對我說出這句話呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.99,0:18:20.27,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}我想弄清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.47,0:18:23.20,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}就算不適合
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.13,0:18:27.59,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}我還是想繼續做這份工作
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.02,0:18:40.83,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}更衣室裡有毛巾
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.97,0:18:43.68,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}不管怎麼說 她…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.02,0:18:46.19,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}我覺得薇爾莉特當不了人偶
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.04,0:18:49.02,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}雖然我們公司剛成立不久
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.26,0:18:51.09,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}給嘉德麗雅的委託卻能源源不絕
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.71,0:18:54.45,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}但是 一旦這時候風評下降
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.66,0:18:56.65,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}好不容易發展起來的事業就…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.27,0:18:58.88,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}還是辭掉薇爾莉特比較好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.32,0:19:00.90,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}不 再稍微…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.39,0:19:02.25,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}我說
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.23,0:19:06.29,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}埃麗卡 薇爾莉特也在
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.75,0:19:08.21,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}你們這是怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.01,0:19:10.81,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}我覺得…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.41,0:19:13.97,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}我覺得沒必要讓她辭職
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.07,0:19:19.25,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}薇爾莉特她打字準確又迅速
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.65,0:19:22.88,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}填寫收件人名和製作名冊都做得很好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.63,0:19:27.07,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}假以時日 學會更多東西
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.03,0:19:31.09,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}肯定能漸漸學會寫信
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.39,0:19:36.91,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}求您了 請不要辭退她
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.43,0:19:39.35,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}矛盾了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.71,0:19:43.27,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}你明明說過我不適合這份任務
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.57,0:19:45.55,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}矛盾了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.49,0:19:59.31,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}不適合當自動手記人偶的人是我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.59,0:20:04.79,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}所以這麼拚命地袒護她
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.28,0:20:12.26,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}如今打字機的原型
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.92,0:20:17.23,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}是活版印刷界的權威 奧蘭多博士發明的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.60,0:20:23.94,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}他的妻子身為小說家卻不幸失明 無法執筆
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.20,0:20:26.45,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}為妻子茉莉製作的這台機器
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.30,0:20:30.81,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}博士將其命名為「自動手記人偶」
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.78,0:20:35.82,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}現在則變成整個代筆行業的代稱
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.71,0:20:38.87,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}遇見她我才真正感受到
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.39,0:20:42.01,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}幾乎被自己遺忘的夢想
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.77,0:20:46.06,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}以及埋在內心深處的真實想法
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.59,0:20:51.39,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}如同奧蘭多夫人寫的小說震撼了我的心靈一般
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.72,0:20:55.80,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}要關門了 沒關係嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.10,0:20:56.67,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.65,0:21:03.20,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}總有一天
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.25,0:21:11.04,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}我也想寫出足以打動人心的 美麗的書信
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.36,0:21:18.57,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}完成
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.81,0:21:20.51,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.40,0:21:24.20,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}很好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.41,0:21:26.31,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}薇爾莉特 站起來看看
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.77,0:21:27.39,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.55,0:21:36.81,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}很適合你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.21,0:21:39.78,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}我的眼光果然不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.04,0:21:43.70,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}還有 拿著這個
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.51,0:21:45.65,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}抱歉這麼晚才給你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.18,0:21:49.05,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}打開看看
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.45,0:21:52.09,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}我打開了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.31,0:21:57.09,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}就是這個
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.90,0:21:59.90,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}是少佐送給我的胸針
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.42,0:22:02.35,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}它流入黑市了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.64,0:22:05.42,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}應該是有人從你的行李裡偷走了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.83,0:22:15.07,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}對了 薇爾莉特
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.29,0:22:17.87,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}要不要去人偶的培訓講座學習下呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.01,0:22:21.99,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}還有短期講座 愛麗絲也去過哦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.29,0:22:24.95,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}老師可是很嚴厲哦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.17,0:22:26.65,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}我覺得對你很有幫助
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.77,0:22:33.79,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}就是為了把它買回來 這個月的工資才沒了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.41,0:22:36.03,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}感激不盡
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.71,0:22:42.49,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}話說 那孩子說的少佐是誰
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.83,0:22:49.14,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}他叫基爾伯特
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.18,0:22:54.47,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}是我在士官學校就結交的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.35,0:22:57.14,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}他出身於布干維爾一族
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.32,0:22:59.63,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}啊 那個邊疆伯爵的…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.39,0:23:09.42,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}明明是個富貴人家的小少爺
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.68,0:23:11.23,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}當時倒還挺有骨氣的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.87,0:23:12.92,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}當時？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.40,0:23:36.33,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}他已經
