Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.21,0:24:29.62,VIOLET_edjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur7.5}優しさで編み続けた
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.88,0:24:35.26,VIOLET_edjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur7.5}ゆりかごで明日へ行こう
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.40,0:24:41.29,VIOLET_edjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur7.5}晴れの日も雨の日にも
Dialogue: 0,0:24:41.61,0:24:45.98,VIOLET_edjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur7.5}あなたを守るために
Dialogue: 0,0:24:46.46,0:24:56.89,VIOLET_edjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur7.5}かけがえのない宝物
Dialogue: 0,0:24:57.47,0:25:07.71,VIOLET_edjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur7.5}名前のない花は　静かに眠るよ
